Author: TiinyTunes
Text: I wish there were more noodles and less soy protein. But it's amazing. I also eat it from the top instead of dumping it into a bowl cuz it seems oily or something, but the flavor. Ohmg. Love love love it. I need to find the other one with konjac noodles. I only saw the pad thai and a taco filling one at aldi in the clearance section.
